1
00:00:01,660 --> 00:00:02,660
Cereal?

2
00:00:02,760 --> 00:00:03,760
What is this stuff?

3
00:00:04,160 --> 00:00:04,680
Notes?

4
00:00:05,180 --> 00:00:06,180
Flakes?

5
00:00:06,440 --> 00:00:08,020
Is there a prize inside?

6
00:00:08,300 --> 00:00:10,320
The prize is you don't starve to death.

7
00:00:10,980 --> 00:00:11,980
Ring it up.

8
00:00:12,280 --> 00:00:18,480
And instead of Oreos, Ginger Snaps,
or Chips Ahoy, we got... Cookie?

9
00:00:18,800 --> 00:00:20,160
That's right, cookie.

10
00:00:20,440 --> 00:00:22,420
Not cookies, cookie.

11
00:00:22,780 --> 00:00:25,420
A big bag with one cookie in it.

12
00:00:26,240 --> 00:00:27,980
Ooh, Mama, can I have some cookie?

13
00:00:28,640 --> 00:00:30,020
Yeah, but only two bites.

14
00:00:30,480 --> 00:00:32,820
Don't suck out all the chips like you did
last time.

15
00:00:34,440 --> 00:00:39,160
When it came to soap, instead of zest,
dial, or coast, we got...

16
00:00:39,161 --> 00:00:41,700
KMA, do you have a problem with that?

17
00:00:42,690 --> 00:00:43,690
Ring it up.

18
00:00:44,020 --> 00:00:47,700
My mother could save money a lot of
places, but not on her ass.

